==Turkish==
===Accusativus===
'''-ı''' (''with back vowel harmony'')

'''-i''' (''with front vowel harmony'')

Other forms: -u, -ü (if last vocal is o,ö,u or ü), -yı, -yi, -yu, -yü (after a vocal), -nı, -ni, -nu, -nü (after possessive)

Examples:
ev-i, araba-yı, yol-u, babası-nı